This plugin requires a little extra attention to build.  As far as I can tell,
Borland does not publish their SDK in a maven repo.  In order to build, you
need to download the SDK from
http://www.borland.com/products/downloads/download_starteam.html.

Then:

tar xzvf StarTeamSDK-2008.tar.gz
cd sdk
mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=com.borland -DartifactId=starteam100 -Dpackaging=jar -Dversion=10 -Dfile=lib/starteam100.jar
mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=com.borland -DartifactId=starteam100-resources -Dpackaging=jar -Dversion=10 -Dfile=lib/starteam100-resources.jar
mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=com.smartsockets -DartifactId=ss -Dpackaging=jar -Dversion=1 -Dfile=lib/ss.jar

After that, the mvn targets should work as you generally expect them to.
